SOL Phenduka and MacG are ready to take over the United Kingdom. The hosts of Podcast and Chill with MacG, whose real names are Solomzi Phenduka (35) and Macgyver Mukwevho (34), are preparing to travel to the United Kingdom for their MacG and Friends UK Tour. They will be entertaining their fans at venues with DJ sets, with both pre-party and after-party performances. The shows start on Friday 15 July in Manchester, after which they will be performing an exclusive DJ set in London. The tour will close on Sunday 17 July in Birmingham. They will be doing a live recording of their podcast at the Birmingham show, followed by an after-party to say goodbye to their fans. ALSO READ: Jerusalema singer flies Mzansi flag high! Sol said it was not their first tour as a podcast. “It’s my first international tour as a DJ but as a podcast, we have been doing tours and recording abroad,” he said. Sol said they have been preparing their sets for a month or two, as they had many people following them in the UK. He said they had a huge following abroad and their fans should expect more exclusive sets around the world.